{"type": "article", "id": 15298, "title": "《The Danger of Music and Other Anti-Utopian Essays》", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 1218, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604230602zuBUSToMAEcdk69w.jpg\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"1.49944873\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Danger-Music-Other-Anti-Utopian-Essays/dp/0520268059/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1442798908&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=the+danger+of+music\" target=\"_blank\">《The Danger of Music and Other Anti-Utopian Essays》</a>，\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tRichard Taruskin, 2010\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这本书就是乐评集。Richard Taruskin 不是一般的乐评人，他是厚到砖头都不足以形容的<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Oxford-History-Western-Music-5-vol-ebook/dp/B004H0N71S/ref=sr_1_2?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1442807454&amp;sr=8-2&amp;keywords=oxford+history+of+music\">五卷本《牛津西方音乐史》</a>的作者。当我对写字一事感到沮丧时，这本书和以下要介绍的另一本书是最好的灯塔。它们让我明白好的写作是超越题材和体裁的。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}